## Database Schema Quick Reference

### Critical Keys & Relationships
```sql
Users (PK: UserID) → Enrollments.UserID, QuizResults.UserID, ForumPosts.UserID
Courses (PK: CourseID) → Enrollments.CourseID, Quizzes.CourseID, ForumPosts.CourseID
Quizzes (PK: QuizID) → Questions.QuizID, QuizResults.QuizID
Questions (PK: QuestionID) → QuestionOptions.QuestionID
```

### Unique Constraints to Verify
```sql
-- These must be unique
Users.Username UNIQUE
Users.Email UNIQUE

-- These should form composite unique
Enrollments (UserID, CourseID) - user should only enroll once per course
QuestionOptions (QuestionID, OptionLabel) - labels must be unique per question
```

---

## Build & Fix Cycle

### Step 1: Reproduce the Bug
```powershell
# Build fresh
MSBuild.exe "MindSpace.sln" /p:Configuration=Debug

# Start server
iisexpress.exe /path:".\MindSpace" /port:8080

# Access specific page that shows bug
# Open browser DevTools (F12) → Console tab
```

### Step 2: Check Error Details
- **Browser Console:** JavaScript errors
- **Visual Studio Output:** Debug logs, compiler warnings
- **Web.config:** `<customErrors mode="Off" />` shows errors in browser
- **Application Insights (if configured):** Server-side exceptions

### Step 3: Write Fix & Verify
```csharp
// Before fix: test what breaks
DataTable dt = DatabaseHelper.ExecuteQuery(sql, prms);
int value = Convert.ToInt32(dt.Rows[0]["Column"]); // BUG: crashes on NULL

// After fix: test that works
DataTable dt = DatabaseHelper.ExecuteQuery(sql, prms);
int value = (dt.Rows[0]["Column"] == DBNull.Value) ? 0 : Convert.ToInt32(dt.Rows[0]["Column"]); // FIXED
```

### Step 4: Commit with Context
```
Format: [BUGFIX] Descriptive title

Body:
- Root cause: explain why this was broken
- Reproduction: steps to see the bug
- Solution: what changed and why it fixes it
- Verification: how to test the fix works
```

---

## Security Checklist for Fixes

- [ ] SQL: All queries use parameterized statements (no string concatenation)
- [ ] Auth: Session checks in Page_Load before any logic
- [ ] Input: All form inputs validated server-side (not just client-side)
- [ ] Output: User input encoded when displayed (XSS prevention)
- [ ] Passwords: Hashed with salt before storage (using DatabaseHelper.HashPassword)
- [ ] HTTPS: Consider enforcing in Web.config if deployed

---

## Performance Checklist for Fixes

- [ ] Database: Queries use indexes, avoid SELECT *
- [ ] Caching: ViewState not excessively large
- [ ] Lazy Loading: DataTables loaded only when needed (not in Page_Load)
- [ ] Batch Operations: Multiple inserts combined, not looped
- [ ] Async: Consider async/await if long-running operations
- [ ] Cleanup: Dispose of SqlConnection, SqlCommand properly (using statements)

---

## File Structure for Bug Fixes
```
MindSpace/
├── App_Code/
│   └── DatabaseHelper.cs            # Database access - central issue source
├── [role]/
│   ├── *.aspx.cs                    # Code-behind logic - bugs here
│   └── *.aspx                       # Markup validation issues
├── Web.config                       # Connection string, session config
└── Properties/
    └── AssemblyInfo.cs              # Version info, strong name
```

