## Quick Debugging Commands

```powershell
# Check build errors
MSBuild.exe "MindSpace.sln" /p:Configuration=Debug /v:detailed

# Monitor database
sqlcmd -S (localdb)\MSSQLLocalDB -d MindSpaceDB
# Then run SELECT queries to inspect data

# Inspect session in code
Response.Write(string.Format("UserID: {0}, Role: {1}", 
    Session["UserID"], Session["Role"]));

# Check browser network tab (F12 → Network)
# Look for 500 errors, failed requests, slow responses
```

